  • Classes in org.sidif.triple used by org.sidif.parser 
    Class and Description
    Triple
    http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Triple states about a Triple "The atomic data entity in the Resource Description Framework" "as it is based upon the idea of making statements about resources (in particular web resources) in the form of subject–predicate–object expressions. " this is a more generic Triple concept that does not depend on the technical details of RDF
